Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我總覺得我那包是假的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好，是時候進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡有？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會是把自己的鐵筒\N跟我的交換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了，良牙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我又開始覺得我本來那包才是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可是哪包才是我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好，是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,歸根究底都是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直這樣下去也不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而且本來就不知道哪包才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好，這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說，我的是真品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要高興還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那可能本來就是我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,還我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊是下玻道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,熱水…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,才不輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你阻礙我了，走開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都阻礙我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你才要滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的鐵筒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這下子不用做豬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，你開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛，這根本就沒治好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,騙子，騙子，騙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,各位好可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,說回來，溶水後不立即用就沒效果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼重要的事應該再說清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,算吧，大家都還是原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒變奇怪的東西就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好遲呢，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這真是生物學上劃時代的大發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,交給現場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是圓澤山中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,被認為已在古早時期絕種的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,劍齒虎和翼恐龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,（請稍候）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊是東京的錄影室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,高木先生？現場的高木先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,發表！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,新的無差別格鬥早乙女流的繼承人是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是良牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,早乙女流的繼續人是良牙？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:43.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}因為今天下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:51.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}我沒遵守約定 留在家中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:59.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}對不起 不是我討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:04.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}只是想這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:14.00,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}在房屋插了一朵花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:22.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}露水滴下來 就像眼淚般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:30.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}還好不是雛罌粟花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:38.66,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}因為不能開得太天真無邪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:45.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}無名之花 就像我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:56.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\be1\fsp1}孤單地 一個人在禱告
